summary: This new code file, moviepage5.html, contributes a specific movie page to the system. It includes HTML elements for displaying movie information such as the movie title, poster, summary, and a video trailer. Additionally, it allows users to rate the movie with a star rating system and submit their ratings. The file also introduces a navigation menu with links to other pages in the system. The file predominantly focuses on presenting movie details and interaction for user feedback within the software system.
